ium heat. Pan fry burgers in batches (approx. 3-4 min per side). Transfer to paper towels to drain."},{"content":"To serve, build burgers on buns to taste, with vegan mayonnaise, mustard, lettuce, sliced tomatoes and sliced onions."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Cook long grain brown rice before starting recipe. Place 32 oz water into mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket and weigh in 7 oz brown rice. Remove simmering basket with spatula and rinse rice under cold running water. Place simmering basket with rice into mixing bowl and rinse <strong>5 sec\/speed 5<\/strong> then cook <strong>50 min\/212°F\/speed 4<\/strong>. Set aside and start recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","1h 40m","8 portions"]}